data.description: Step inside and feel the vibe! New flooring, fun paint colors and updates to main level, kitchen, and lower level make this great home move-in ready! With three bedrooms conveniently located on the main level, this home offers both comfort and convenience. A great entertaining space in the lower level comes with amazing shelving and electric fireplace.  Summer nights and backyard lights await you with a 6ft privacy fence newly installed since purchase.  This move in ready charmer is a must see!
